# unit/

BATS test suite for Intent CLI covering all commands and subsystems. Tests are organized by command domain and include infrastructure tests, configuration validation, project operations, and core features like steel threads, backlog, and Claude integration.

## Files

- `basic.bats` -- Infrastructure and test helper verification
- `global_commands.bats` -- Global commands (version, help, doctor, info, bootstrap)
- `init_commands.bats` -- Project initialization and setup
- `config.bats` -- Configuration loading and PROJECT_ROOT detection
- `bootstrap.bats` -- Bootstrap installation and global config
- `help_commands.bats` -- Help system and command documentation
- `project_commands.bats` -- Commands that require project context
- `st_commands.bats` -- Steel thread lifecycle (new, list, show, move, delete)
- `bl_commands.bats` -- Backlog command integration and task bridging
- `task_commands.bats` -- Task creation and backlog synchronization
- `agent_commands.bats` -- Claude subagent installation and management
- `skills_commands.bats` -- Claude skills lifecycle (list, install, sync, uninstall)
- `test_autopsy.bats` -- intent-autopsy skill installation and directory handling
- `test_diogenes.bats` -- Diogenes subagent and intent-elixir-testing skill
- `migration.bats` -- Migration utilities and backup functionality
- `fileindex_commands.bats` -- File indexing utility with checkbox tracking
- `treeindex_commands.bats` -- Directory summary generation via Claude AI
